838
01:06:09.089 --> 01:06:10.215
[grunts]

839
01:06:14.469 --> 01:06:16.346
Oh. my God! Oh. my God!

840
01:06:16.429 --> 01:06:17.430
[Maria yelling]

841
01:06:18.807 --> 01:06:19.891
[man yells]

842
01:06:27.691 --> 01:06:28.733
[Asia] Fuck!

843
01:06:28.817 --> 01:06:29.818
[grunts]

844
01:06:33.238 --> 01:06:34.280
