867
01:07:41.848 --> 01:07:43.016
[Maria] Yes.

868
01:07:43.099 --> 01:07:45.060
Splendid.

869
01:07:45.143 --> 01:07:47.604
You will pledge to our Lord.

870
01:07:47.687 --> 01:07:52.567
