991
01:18:28.369 --> 01:18:29.245
[grunts]

992
01:18:36.752 --> 01:18:37.837
Dude.

993
01:18:38.629 --> 01:18:39.630
[growls]

994
01:18:39.714 --> 01:18:41.340
