[The Head as Maria]
Hey. Butthead.

1027
01:22:10.841 --> 01:22:12.843
you should have left me.

1028
01:22:12.927 --> 01:22:14.595
I'd still be alive.

1029
01:22:15.804 --> 01:22:17.932
