1067
01:25:28.205 --> 01:25:30.207
[dramatic music playing]

1068
01:25:37.965 --> 01:25:40.801
[dramatic music playing]

1069
01:25:46.265 --> 01:25:49.601
[Asia grunts. pants]

1070
01:25:49.685 --> 01:25:51.520
[alarm ringing]

1071
